      <h1>AI Chatbots for Lead Generation: When They're Worth It</h1>
      <p><strong>Nearly every article ranking for "AI chatbots for lead generation" is published by a company selling one.</strong> This is an independent look instead — not a ranked list of vendors, but a framework for deciding whether a chatbot actually helps your specific lead generation setup, and what to check before choosing one if it does.</p>
